====Usage notes====
Unlike most words beginning with consonantal y {{IPAchar|/j/}}, this word triggers {{m|fr|liaison}} with valid preceding words. Eg:
* les yeux {{IPAchar|/le.z‿jø/}}
* les grands yeux {{IPAchar|/le.ɡʁɑ̃.z‿jø/}}
* Il a de beaux yeux {{IPAchar|/i.l‿ad.bo.z‿jø/}}
